sentences.english: None of this will actually be decided at Bali.
sentences.chinese: 所有這一切實際上都決定在巴里島。

sentences.english: Everything you have ever known Kratos, will now suffer because of your sacrilege .
sentences.chinese: 你要知道你現在所遭受的一切是來自於你的褻瀆。

sentences.english: Where all is obscure and unrealized the best similitude is a dream.
sentences.chinese: 一切都是模糊而非現實的，酷似一場夢。

sentences.english: Some day his pictures will be worth more than all you have in your shop.
sentences.chinese: 有一天，他的畫會比你店裏所有的一切還值錢。

sentences.english: Chinese people has never regarded human beings as the hightest creature among everything else since ancient times.
sentences.chinese: 中華民族自古以來從來不把人看作高於一切。

sentences.english: The team of contributors is generally responsible for the project area and everything in it.
sentences.chinese: 貢獻者組成的團隊一般負責該項目區域和其中的一切。

sentences.english: Economic construction is an overriding task of China.
sentences.chinese: 經濟建設是中國壓倒一切的中心任務。

sentences.english: Because of how you reacted in the morning.
sentences.chinese: 一切皆由你早上的反應而起。

sentences.english: You're mad because he lied to you.
sentences.chinese: 你因爲他對你撒了個謊就氣得不顧一切了。

sentences.english: None of it could have happened without off-the-charts courage.
sentences.chinese: 如果他沒有過人的勇氣，這一切都不可能發生。

sentences.english: Thou annointest my day with pep; my mug runneth over.
sentences.chinese: 你宣告了我充沛的一天，一切的疲憊必然消失不見。

sentences.english: He does exceedingly abundantly above and beyond what we could ever ask, imagine or think!
sentences.chinese: 神能充充足足的成就一切，超過我們所求所想的。

sentences.english: But Cho refused to accept that, not wanting to lose the protectorate .
sentences.chinese: 但喬拒絕接受這一切，他不想失去保護權。

sentences.english: Of course, this is all just a fantasy.
sentences.chinese: 當然，這一切都還是空想。

sentences.english: Seemingly, looking in from the outside, I had everything.
sentences.chinese: 表面上看，我擁有了一切。

sentences.english: Knowing that all is well within me.
